show.title: My Sister Stole My Man
show.sharing_text: हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा
show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा 
https://kukufm.com/show/my-sister-stole-my-man/?utm_source=share_sh
show.description: What begins as a fateful encounter spirals into a web of deception when a woman's sister steals her identity after a passionate one-night stand. Six years later, destiny intervenes as she becomes the legal advisor to the very CEO she once shared that unforgettable night with. As their professional relationship blossoms into something deeper, her sister—desperate to protect her stolen life—orchestrates a series of increasingly dangerous sabotage attempts. With each thwarted plot, the CEO grows more determined to uncover the truth behind the woman who's captured his heart. In this thrilling tale of betrayal, redemption, and second chances, buried secrets finally surface, leading to a shocking revelation that reunites a family torn apart by lies and brings two souls back to where they were always meant to be.
